WEBVTT

00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:10.052
This is what I have for you. I want to show you, starting off, one of the prophetic words that I've given you all in prayer was about the fish.

00:00:10.053 --> 00:00:22.418
Do you remember I said I saw the fish rolling in on the waves? Whenever I was seeing, I saw thousands of fish rolling in, and I said they're coming up from the water.

00:00:22.419 --> 00:00:28.312
I don't know what caused this, but I could just see them, and as they were coming in, they were on the shore.

00:00:28.313 --> 00:00:33.851
There were so many of them, and the Lord told me it's going to stink because there were so many dead fish.

00:00:33.852 --> 00:00:41.795
Well, one of my viewers—I don't know if it was Facebook—somebody sent this and said, "Hey, did you see all the dead fish from the lake?

00:00:41.796 --> 00:00:47.599
It wasn't from the ocean, but this is what's happening."I don't know what would cause this.

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:56.159
They're saying there are pockets where the oxygen in the water is causing them to die, and all this stuff, right?

00:00:56.160 --> 00:01:03.458
But I was seeing all the fish rolling in on the waves. So, this is what I saw.

00:01:03.459 --> 00:01:12.062
I wanted Braden to play this little clip for y'all. Do you see all these dead fish?

00:01:12.063 --> 00:01:18.169
Can they see all these dead fish? This is serious. I don't know what would cause all that, but they're saying maybe oxygen.

00:01:18.170 --> 00:01:20.568
They don't know what's in the water, but something's causing all these fish.

00:01:20.569 --> 00:01:26.876
But this is what the Lord was showing me—another glimpse into the future. And the Lord's warning us of things.

00:01:26.877 --> 00:01:40.078
I even saw this in California, all up the coast, all over Oregon, all over the area—major fish coming in by the thousands, tens of thousands dead on the top of the water.

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:45.493
And that right there is exactly what I was shown. Just like that.

00:01:45.494 --> 00:01:51.903
And it is nasty. But I was like, isn't that amazing? And they don't know what's coming. Maybe they do now.

00:01:51.904 --> 00:02:04.559
This video is a couple days old as I receive this, but I just thought of the prophetic side of it, that as watchmen, the Lord shows us what's coming and we pray over things.

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:16.312
It's pretty amazing how fast things are happening. It's not like before, where we always talked about how things would happen and we would see them, but it would take weeks, months, or years for stuff to manifest.

00:02:16.313 --> 00:02:27.943
Now it's happening in days. Yes! And I'm like, "Wow, Lord, look at the signs of the times."You can stop it if you want to.

00:02:27.944 --> 00:02:34.931
So then the other part was praying over the escalation of war. I heard it again.

00:02:34.932 --> 00:02:43.284
So I'll go over my visitation experience, what happened in my sleep out of nowhere.

00:02:43.285 --> 00:02:52.853
I mean, this is like 5:00 in the morning. I wake up, and I feel the Holy Ghost and fire all over my body.

00:02:52.854 --> 00:02:58.628
As I breathe in, I feel the anointing and the power of the Holy Spirit just flowing through me.

00:02:58.629 --> 00:03:05.119
And all of a sudden—this is what's interesting—it wasn't a dream, but it was a night vision.

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:12.737
That's the only way... I've never had this before, but I was asleep, you know, in between sleep and awake.

00:03:12.738 --> 00:03:21.230
And I'm seeing, and He says to me, "Brandon, I'm asking you to help me with something."And I paused.

00:03:21.231 --> 00:03:45.298
I said, because I'm asleep, "Lord, what can I help you with?"And He said, "There's a youth group across the street."And I saw the youth group, and He said, "There's a young man that's going to be coming to this youth group whom I'm calling into ministry.

00:03:45.299 --> 00:03:56.310
I want him to be in ministry. There's a call on his life, but he doesn't know me yet. Pray for this young man."And I could see this young man.

00:03:56.311 --> 00:04:04.270
He looked like a football player, and it's an actual person—I know that for a fact now after the Lord showed me.

00:04:04.271 --> 00:04:24.351
So the Lord had me praying for this young man, and He said, "I want him to come over to the youth group across the street during the fall, and I've asked other people to do what I'm asking you to do, but they've all told me no."I had saved some money.

00:04:24.352 --> 00:04:30.502
I told Diana we've been saving because we want to remodel our house, but we don't tell everybody because we don't believe in debt.

00:04:30.503 --> 00:04:36.399
We do Financial Peace University. We believe in not borrowing money as much as possible.

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:41.585
If you have to in an emergency, you know, but we believe in paying cash for things.

00:04:41.586 --> 00:04:44.728
That's just the way we've always lived. We don't believe in credit cards.

00:04:44.729 --> 00:04:51.958
We don't believe in things like that. We don't borrow; we're not slave to the lender.

00:04:51.959 --> 00:05:01.951
The only thing is like our student loans or whatever, but I'm just saying paying things down deliberately, living by faith.

00:05:01.952 --> 00:05:07.385
So we wanted to fix up our bathrooms and do things around our house, so we have our own little account.

00:05:07.386 --> 00:05:17.599
We've been putting money in there, and we got it up because we had a guy come out and say, "Hey, this is what it's going to cost to remodel it all, fix up your bathrooms, and update everything."We were really excited about it.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:20.594
It's something private we had between us that we don't talk about.

00:05:20.595 --> 00:05:24.444
So we put some money back—kept putting money back—and the account was getting really big.

00:05:24.445 --> 00:05:29.282
We were excited about it because we had the money to redo what we wanted to have redone.

00:05:29.283 --> 00:05:36.434
Then we had the leak happen in our house, and we were believing God for stuff, you know.

00:05:36.435 --> 00:05:42.971
Well, we put the money back and we didn't say anything, but we were right at that point.

00:05:42.972 --> 00:05:48.292
And the Lord said to me, "Brandon, I've asked these people to help me.

00:05:48.293 --> 00:06:16.998
I know it's above what you tithe, and I know it's above what I've already asked you to do, but could you help with the youth building that they're trying to build?"I said, "Woo, that's hard."I said, "Lord, I told you I'll do anything you ask me to do,"but my flesh was irritated, just being real, because I worked so hard to save that money.

00:06:16.999 --> 00:06:31.832
I told Him, "My flesh is annoyed, but I told you I would do anything you ever asked me to do, so I'll do it."And instantaneously, you deal with...

00:06:31.833 --> 00:06:39.988
I'm just like anybody, y'all, I deal with the flesh too. My flesh was like, "That's my money I've saved.

00:06:39.989 --> 00:06:48.912
And you're asking me to give that?"He said, "I desire it to be done before the fall. I need help. Would you help me?"So I told Diana.

00:06:48.913 --> 00:07:00.588
And Diana, always sweet Diana, goes, "If that's what the Lord is saying, let's just do it."I wanted her to be like, "No, we're not doing that."I thought, "I can blame it on her, Lord.

00:07:00.589 --> 00:07:23.111
See, she said no, it's her fault."But she was so nice about it and said, "Well, if that's what the Lord is saying, honey, let's just do it."I thought, "Please don't say that."I was really mad at her then, I really was, because I wanted to have a scapegoat and say, "You know what, Diana?

00:07:23.112 --> 00:07:33.548
I don't blame you. It's all right,"and then go, "God, it's her problem, she's the one that did it."That's just where I was, just being real, okay?

00:07:33.549 --> 00:07:41.582
I'm just being real. And so, when she said it so nicely, I was just like, "Okay, flesh.

00:07:41.583 --> 00:07:53.111
Okay, flesh."Thank you, God, for an obedient wife who loves the Lord.

00:07:53.112 --> 00:07:59.549
She had a good attitude about it; my attitude was still stinky. I prayed over it for the whole day.

00:07:59.550 --> 00:08:06.082
Then I reached out to the pastor, and I was trying to give hints: "Hey, do you like going out to eat?

00:08:06.083 --> 00:08:14.239
Do you like going to this certain place?"and he acted like he was too busy and didn't want anything to do with it. So I thought, "Well, there's a closed door.

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:20.399
There's a closed door."Because I felt inside that I was going to be obedient, but if he says no, then it's not God.

00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:30.074
I'm not going to give that money then. And so it's not funny. It's really real. And so I say, "Hey, do you like going to Wild Fork?

00:08:30.075 --> 00:08:35.034
Do you want to go out to eat?"He didn't respond, "Oh yeah, it's a good place to eat."But never anything else.

00:08:35.034 --> 00:08:51.594
I thought, "Okay, close call. It's not like I had to give it."It just, you know, we tell you these things. I'm trying to help y'all; it's helping me help.

00:08:51.595 --> 00:09:10.819
So, to make a long story short, I get up and it's Sunday morning and the Lord said, "Not only do I want you to give the money, but this time I don't want you to hand it to them to hand to the pastor personally and give them this check.

00:09:10.820 --> 00:09:18.231
You are to try to deflect the glory."And he corrected me on some things. This is where I'm going to go with it.

00:09:18.232 --> 00:09:25.198
He said, "This is not to give you glory about how much money you're going to give to the youth program for this building.

00:09:25.199 --> 00:09:37.665
I want you to do this privately, and I want you to put it in the bucket and just let that check sit in that bucket, and you're not going to get any man's praise at all.

00:09:37.666 --> 00:09:46.216
Not a thank you from them personally, like, 'Please pray over this seed.'Do you understand?

00:09:46.217 --> 00:09:51.910
This is a huge deal for us."And so my flesh was like—when he said that, I was even more disturbed.

00:09:51.911 --> 00:10:00.953
I went, "Are you kidding me?"So, I sat on the back row like I always do, and that bucket came by.

00:10:00.954 --> 00:10:09.876
And I was like, "I'm looking for a Holy Ghost choir, like an Abraham experience saying, 'Don't kill the son. It's okay.

00:10:09.877 --> 00:10:17.715
I've heard the angel come.'You're looking for the angel to say—the parting of the sky and looking for the angel to go, 'It's okay.

00:10:17.716 --> 00:10:24.665
You don't have to give it. I see your heart.'"But that didn't happen. It didn't happen.

00:10:24.666 --> 00:10:29.450
And as I put that money in the bucket, I saw it go down the aisle and I was looking at it.

00:10:29.451 --> 00:10:33.971
I followed that usher all the way down to the end of the thing where he was taking it up to the altar.

00:10:33.972 --> 00:10:37.736
And I was sitting there watching that usher as close as I could. And I knew where my bucket was.

00:10:37.737 --> 00:10:53.401
And I was watching it, and the Lord said, "Brandon, let it go."I said, "Oh, Father, I give unto you. I don't give it to man."And as I did it, I did it by faith.

00:10:53.402 --> 00:11:08.634
But the thing was, the Lord was showing me there are so many times we're asking to go to the next level, but we don't want to let go of what was past and what we had.

00:11:08.635 --> 00:11:14.004
But if you want to go to the next level with the Father, it takes sacrificial giving.

00:11:14.005 --> 00:11:21.813
It takes the extra. How big is your want-to? How bad do you want change to come in your life, even if it's painful?

00:11:21.814 --> 00:11:30.514
Does that make sense? That's where it wasn't me. He asked for a lot, but every seed produces after its own kind.

00:11:30.515 --> 00:11:39.759
And seedtime and harvest doesn't cease. And if you want to go to a next level, you've got to sow in a level that you've never given before.

00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:46.159
You've given at these levels and you've been faithful with it, but I'm trying to take you somewhere deeper and bigger.

00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:53.439
And I said in my heart, then there are situations inside of me of what I'm believing for from Megan.

00:11:53.440 --> 00:12:01.439
I'm putting a mandate on the seed. I'm calling my seed, naming my seed of what I'm believing for.

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:27.919
Not just material for a bathroom remodel or whatever, but for exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think in these last days—for impartation, for the anointing, for finances, for whatever we're believing for for our own ministry, as you sow into the young man that the Lord gives me the picture of and says, "This is what I desire."And then he spoke to me.

00:12:27.920 --> 00:12:38.203
He said, "I told you I'm coming. The urgency is not there with my body."I said, "Well, Lord, I know you tell me all the time you're coming.

00:12:38.204 --> 00:12:53.596
We tell the people through the channel; I warn them."He said, "But the urgency... Do you know I'm coming?"I said, "Yes, Lord, I thought I did.

00:12:53.597 --> 00:13:05.274
I've said it enough."But as I keep praying over it and he shows me, he said, "Great war is coming."I saw great war.

00:13:05.274 --> 00:13:12.420
He said, "Do you understand great war is coming? You're running out of time for what I've called you to do.

00:13:12.421 --> 00:13:20.742
Out of all these people, obedience to be quick to obey. Be quick to obey."And I was quick within a window.

00:13:20.743 --> 00:13:25.439
I was quick, but in my flesh, like I said, I was squirming like a worm.

00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:32.072
But I did it. But it's not always easy to do what your flesh doesn't want to do.

00:13:32.073 --> 00:13:47.679
And sometimes I said, "Lord, I know the Bible says to be willing and obedient, you'll eat the good of the land."And I'm trying so hard to be willing and obedient, even whenever I'm dealing with flesh.

00:13:47.680 --> 00:14:17.599
But after he showed me the young man and the youth coming across the street getting saved, he said, "I'm asking for my people to help me, but there's not many."And he said, "Brandon, I knew you would."I felt ashamed, even with my attitude.

00:14:17.600 --> 00:14:30.233
Something so materialistic when it's just the Father wanting you to help, and he asks you so politely, "Would you please help me? I need help.

00:14:30.234 --> 00:14:49.679
I desire for these young kids to come across the street to this new youth facility, and that's what's going to attract them to come over here and be curious about what I'm doing across the street, to draw them in with the new net."And yeah, it's a sacrifice for you, but I'm looking for his heart.

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:56.317
And I don't know, ladies and gentlemen. It's just I'm trying to tell you what I'm dealing with.

00:14:56.317 --> 00:15:07.709
It sounds probably so fleshy to some of you, and it's like, "Oh, Brandon, grow up."But it's something that I deal with, and I'm just really transparent.

00:15:07.710 --> 00:15:15.227
But in the part of just doing the sacrifice and going from glory to glory, because the Lord's saying acceleration's coming.

00:15:15.228 --> 00:15:19.699
He keeps talking to me about everything's going to change in this 24-hour period.

00:15:19.700 --> 00:15:24.731
Everything will change, Brandon. Everything that you've ever known is about to change.

00:15:24.731 --> 00:15:28.965
The world is going to go into birthing pains like you've never seen before.

00:15:28.966 --> 00:15:38.039
It's not going to be like Christianity normal. It's going to be Christianity, but not normal.

00:15:38.040 --> 00:15:41.784
What's about to happen, folks—we're about to see things we've never seen before.

00:15:41.785 --> 00:15:49.266
We can see it. Earthquakes, volcanoes. Look at Russia, they had another one, seven point something yesterday.

00:15:49.267 --> 00:15:55.390
And the Lord said, "Watch the Ring of Fire."Watch it for what? And Braden made a short about it.

00:15:55.391 --> 00:16:00.632
He said, "What's happening in the natural, Daddy?"We talked about—he brought that out again.

00:16:00.633 --> 00:16:06.698
He said, "Remember what you prophesied about this? What's happening in the natural is going to happen in the spiritual.

00:16:06.699 --> 00:16:14.076
A shaking in the natural, a shaking in the spiritual, which is going to bring forth the major revival."And he showed his short to me.

00:16:14.077 --> 00:16:29.999
I go, "I forgot the Lord said that."I said, "That's really cool, Braden."So, he showed it to me and I was excited about it, because I'm telling y'all, I keep seeing an escalation of things for a major revival, a major shaking on the Ring of Fire over Asia.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:46.554
"Look and keep watching and praying over Asia, for I've not forgotten my Asian people."And I said, "Well, what's that have to do with Russia?""Well, Dad, part of Russia is part of Asia."And I went, "Well, duh."But I thought that was kind of cool.

00:16:46.555 --> 00:16:58.914
Eastern Asia or whatever. Yeah, Eastern Russia. Up there. And he said, "That's part of Asia."And I thought, "Well, yeah, isn't that amazing?"A shaking in Russia.

00:16:58.915 --> 00:17:13.999
And even in the word that was given, he said, "A shaking in Russia, a major move of God in Russia, a major move of God in Japan, a major move of God in China, a major move of God in South Korea.

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:27.297
I'm bringing down the Iron Curtain in North Korea, and I'll reach my people of North Korea."I'm giving you a window of opportunity, a short window, to reach the people of North Korea, for the Iron Curtain will not stay down for very long.

00:17:27.298 --> 00:17:31.157
But when this window of opportunity opens, it will be flooded.

00:17:31.158 --> 00:17:39.648
And I'm going to give it to you, and many people will be born again in this timeframe. And it will spread, and I'm telling you, over Africa...

00:17:39.649 --> 00:17:49.540
I've seen a major harvest of souls over Africa, all throughout South America, and all throughout Europe. Number one, it wasn't number three.

00:17:49.541 --> 00:17:58.020
What I'm going to say today, Diana said, 'Did you see the pope says he wants revival with the youth?'This is exactly what I saw.

00:17:58.021 --> 00:18:09.897
I saw the pope going through and trying to bring in the younger generation because the Catholic Church was dying with the older generation, trying to bring in the younger crowd.

00:18:09.898 --> 00:18:19.434
'How do we get the young ones in?'Because the older ones, the gray-haired people, are going home to be with the Lord. They're going home; the people are dying.

00:18:19.435 --> 00:18:42.917
And he said, 'How do we bring in the young ones?'And I saw a South Korean flag, and I thought, 'This is exactly what the Lord told me: a revival.'And He said, 'Pray for the harvest of souls over Rome, over Italy, and over these areas for a major move of God in the Catholic Church.'A major move of God in the Catholic Church.

00:18:42.918 --> 00:18:55.044
There are 1.4 billion people in the Catholic Church, and I thought, what a time to have a major revival, an awakening unto God in the Catholic Church and all these other churches that are associated.

00:18:55.045 --> 00:19:17.465
Because I was talking to our pastor and talking about this window of what the Lord was showing me about Adam's lease coming up and believing for that coming from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, to believe for this window of opportunity that God's given us.

00:19:17.466 --> 00:19:29.588
We're at that point of the waterfall, we're right there, but bringing the church together as a whole: the Baptists, the Methodists, the Catholics, the Charismatics, the Episcopalians, whoever.

00:19:29.589 --> 00:19:39.365
I mean, all of us all together being a body, and I saw it was like at war times, a shaking in the church like we've never seen before.

00:19:39.366 --> 00:19:47.797
And I'm telling you all, there's a storm. There's a storm, and the Lord keeps talking about this storm to me over and over again.

00:19:47.798 --> 00:19:54.274
A major wake-up call, major things. And some people say, 'Brandon, are you focused on fear?'No, I'm not focused on fear.

00:19:54.275 --> 00:20:00.677
I'm not afraid at all. I'm looking at Him, staying vertical, and doing what He's asked me to do.

00:20:00.678 --> 00:20:07.195
Even when it's painful, like my story—it's painful to the flesh—but just doing what He's asked you to do.

00:20:07.196 --> 00:20:15.986
And I'm trying to tell y'all to go to the next level. If you be willing and obedient, you'll eat the good of the land.

00:20:15.987 --> 00:20:23.145
If you are obedient to what God has called you to do, it's not always going to be comfortable to your flesh.

00:20:23.146 --> 00:20:32.136
But the test He's talking about—because I said, 'Where are You at in this?'He said, 'Brandon, I'm silent. It's a test. I'm testing to see what you're going to do.

00:20:32.137 --> 00:20:38.062
Are you going to do what I told you to do?'It's quiet in there when you're at school and you're taking the test.

00:20:38.063 --> 00:20:44.257
It's quiet in there because there wasn't the holy angel choirs I was looking for, or even a really good word, a prophetic word, a splitting of the...

00:20:44.258 --> 00:20:51.839
'Okay, You're going to download something to me now.'Nothing. Shh. Quiet during the test.

00:20:51.840 --> 00:20:58.731
So many people don't pass the test because of lack of obedience to what He's called you to do.

00:20:58.732 --> 00:21:05.439
And that's what He said: 'If you're asking Me for so much, how did you think you were going to get there? You're asking Me for so much, Brandon.

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:18.832
How did you think you were going to get there?'It's acceleration, acclimation, acceleration, acclimation. You go from glory to glory. He's changing us, changing us.

00:21:18.833 --> 00:21:29.643
And then He said to me, when I told you I got that—and I'll even tell you the amount, I have no shame about it—I had it from one preacher.

00:21:29.644 --> 00:21:37.616
He said to me, 'I want to bless you with this.'No, the Lord said, 'Don't do that.'He said, 'I want to bless you with this.'He said, 'Don't accept that money.'Remember I told you all that?

00:21:37.617 --> 00:21:42.924
And He said, 'I don't want you to do that. I don't want you to accept that.'And He said, 'I don't want you to take that.

00:21:42.925 --> 00:21:51.316
There are doors that I'm telling you to walk through where I'm standing on the other side of them, but there are some doors where I'm not there, Brandon.

00:21:51.317 --> 00:21:56.479
They'll present themselves to you, but you only go through the doors that I tell you to go through.

00:21:56.480 --> 00:22:04.639
Only follow the voice of God.'But instantaneously, whenever He tests you about a gift and says, 'Don't accept that.

00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:13.758
Don't take that,'and I'm like, 'Well, Lord, that's a blessing. I'd like to receive that.''No, give it back.'Okay.

00:22:13.759 --> 00:22:20.955
Then He comes to you in your sleep and says, 'I want you to give the biggest gift you've ever given,'and all of it in the same week.

00:22:20.956 --> 00:22:28.288
And you're going, 'Dear Lord, You're stretching me, but You're asking for so much.

00:22:28.289 --> 00:22:35.870
You're asking me for so much.'You have to level up. It's like you do in a game: you level up, and you go from glory to glory.

00:22:35.871 --> 00:22:40.633
You level up, and you're able to handle more and more as you accelerate with the Lord.

00:22:40.634 --> 00:22:43.811
Does that make sense, what I'm trying to tell you all? I hope so.

00:22:43.812 --> 00:22:49.279
I try to get out as best I can what I'm feeling in my spirit to warn you all about today.

00:22:49.280 --> 00:22:56.034
Whenever you're asking the Father for something and you're wanting to go to the next level, He puts you through a test.

00:22:56.035 --> 00:23:04.387
Yes, He puts you through a test. We go from glory to glory. He's changing us, and we're on that potter's wheel, and He's pushing.

00:23:04.388 --> 00:23:10.781
It doesn't always feel comfortable when He's pushing on it, but I want to pass the first time.

00:23:10.782 --> 00:23:15.678
I don't want to wait, because you don't know when the next time is coming around.

00:23:15.679 --> 00:23:22.323
You might say, 'Well, you failed that test,'but just because you fail a test...

00:23:22.324 --> 00:23:28.236
It's not like schools nowadays where if you fail, they just keep passing you because they don't want to deal with you.

00:23:28.237 --> 00:23:33.772
The thing is, God says you're going to pass this test, and you're going to pass it or you're not going to the next level.

00:23:33.773 --> 00:23:42.223
